videos.description: Arizona State's Romello White hits a lay-in and draws the foul after a nice feed inside by Kodi Justice.
videos.headline: Justice's no-look pass sets up White's layup

videos.description: Tra Holder knocks down a deep 3-pointer for Arizona State in the first half against Colorado.
videos.headline: Holder drills 3 from deep

videos.description: Namon Wright takes an inbounds pass in the corner and drills a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Wright knocks down 3 for Buffs

videos.description: Arizona State's rollercoaster season continues as McKinley Wright IV leads Colorado to a 97-85 win over the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: Colorado crushes ASU's NCAA Tournament chances
